title: Did Frito Lai issue a call for a product because of Salmonella's fear?
subtitle: In July and August 2017, the withdrawal of new Freto-Le Jalapino products was reported.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Frito-Lei released a copy of two potato chip producers in April 2017 on concerns related to Salmonella, a report prepared as a new report in July and August 2017.
